data.description: This is a well-maintained two-story home featuring three bedrooms, three bathrooms, and a deep single-car garage with storage shelves. The covered porch leads to a front door opening into a spacious, open-plan living room, dining area, and kitchen. The kitchen boasts ample space with new laminate flooring and new stainless steel appliances. From the kitchen, there's access to the backyard, which includes a dog run and a small storage shed, and offers mountain views from the rear patio. Upstairs, there are three carpeted bedrooms. The master bedroom features walk-in closets, a ceiling fan, and an adjoining master bath. There are two additional bedrooms and a guest bathroom. For convenience, there's an upstairs laundry room. The home is equipped with central air conditioning.
